One green, one blue. It's a mutation.

36
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:20,880
It's a very groovy mutation.

37
00:10:20,990 --> 00:10:24,210
I've got news for you, Amy.
You are a mutant.

38
00:10:24,210 --> 00:10:27,400
First you proposition a girl,
and then you call her deformed.

39
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:29,720
How is that seduction technique working for you?

40
