49
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,340
I'm sorry, one cola.

50
00:10:57,460 --> 00:10:58,480
Charles here was just telling me that I'm

51
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,630
like one of the first sea creatures that grew legs.

52
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,960
Tiny bit sexier.

53
