Oh look, you have heterochromia too!

57
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:17,420
- Say what?
- Look at her eye..

58
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:22,670
Right, Raven get your coat please.

59
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:25,210
Don't talk to me, you did
that on purpose.

60
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:26,540
- I did not!
- Yes you did!

61
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:29,030
Why would I do it on purpose?
You know I can't control it sometimes.

62
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:32,070
- When I'm stressed or tired..
- You seem to be doing a perfectly
good job right now.

63
