A small slip up is one thing.
A big one does not bear thinking about.

70
00:11:58,070 --> 00:12:00,300
"Mutant and proud"

71
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:04,470
"Mutant and proud"?

72
00:12:15,030 --> 00:12:16,790
If only...

73
00:12:22,130 --> 00:12:24,380
- Would you date me?
- Of course I would.

74
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,340
Any young man would be lucky to have you.

75
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:28,630
- You're stunning!
- Looking like this?

76
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:30,530
Like, you...what?

77
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,060
Blue?

78
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:40,430
- You're my oldest friend.
- I'm your only friend.

79
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,270
Thank you for that.

80
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,630
Well?

81
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:47,470
I'm incapable of thinking of you that way,
I feel responsible for you.

82
00:12:47,590 --> 00:12:50,530
Anything else would just feel wrong.

83
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:53,300
- But what if you didn't know me?
- Unfortunately I do know you.

84
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:56,590
I don't know what's got into you lately?
You're awfully concerned with your looks.

85
00:13:01,180 --> 00:13:03,150
I'm sleepy.
Will you read to me?

86
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:05,120
