87
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:08,350
Well fine. Read that new thesis
it always sends me right off.

88
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:12,050
To Homo Neanderthalensis,
his  mutant cousin Homo Sapiens,

89
00:13:12,050 --> 00:13:13,790
was an aberration.

90
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:16,740
Peaceful co-habitation, if ever it existed,

91
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:18,170
was short lived.

92
00:13:18,470 --> 00:13:22,520
Records show, without exception, that the
arrival of the mutated human species

93
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:27,400
