extinction of their less evolved kin.

94
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:39,460
Another day at the office.

95
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,780
Is that Colonel Hendry?

96
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:44,290
- The NATO guy?
- Yeah.

97
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:46,770
Yes it is.

98
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,340
